Scripts used to query the status of PBS or interact with it.

Authors: Charles Blundell (CB)
====

Contents:

- pbs_reserve.sh:  Run it to reserve your machine, forbiding PBS to put jobs on it for some time. Check its usage.
- qjobs:  Returns a list of current jobs on PBS, for each users. (CB)
- qmachs: Returns a list of the machines executing jobs right now (rely on pbsnodes, can be incorrect) (CB)
